title: Anti-Aging Restorative Night Cream - Absolutely Ageless™ Skin Care Collection | AVEENO®
description:
Learn how AVEENO® Absolutely Ageless™ Restorative Night Cream, with ACTIVE NATURALS® Blackberry Complex, improves elasticity and firmness for healthier, younger-looking skin in just one week.

Within 1 week of use, skin looks smoother, younger, and healthier, as it helps to strengthen aging skin’s natural moisture barrier, and reduce the visible effects of elastin and collagen loss.

To learn more about the Absolutely Ageless™ skin care product line, and find the right anti-aging products for your skin, visit: http://www.aveeno.com/category/our+products/collections/absolutely+ageless.do.

For more skin care tips for naturally beautiful skin, subscribe to the AVEENO® channel at: https://www.youtube.com/user/aveeno.
